title.rendered: Trailmax Roller Shutter – Dodge Ram 1500 QUAD CAB

content.rendered:
Trailmax Electric Roller Shutter to suit RAM1500 Quad Cab

 

  • Electric retractable including two wireless remote controls
  • Remote operated internal LED light
  • 100% water proof
  • Durable black powder coat finish
  • Heavy Duty 200kg loading on top
  • incorporated side mounting to accept optional cross bars
  • Compatible with sport bars
  • Safety anti jam function in built
  • Can stop at any opening via remote

 

Amazing 2 year warranty

excerpt.rendered:
